body:
It's best to have as much tests as possible, but I'm not sure the Spark runner needs to test `metrics` backend integration. I would be happy to see this as part of the SDK (maybe as a followup work to the new Metric API).
I'm afraid this will make the runner too "tight" and this also opens the question of "what about CSV sink integration ?", and more sinks contributors might add.
@staslev @jbonofre WDYT  ?
